## Phase 1 — Shared UI Component Library

All components live in `src/components/ui/`. Built with Radix UI primitives + Tailwind + CVA for variants.

### Core Primitives (Extend/New)

| Component | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `Button` | [NEW] | Replaces `GlowButton`. Variants: primary/ghost/outline/destructive. Loading spinner. |
| `Badge` | [NEW] | Tier chips (Free/Student/Pro), status pills (Applied/Pending) |
| `Skeleton` | [NEW] | Used in every data loading state |
| `Toast` | [NEW] | Via Radix `Toast`. Success/error/info. |
| `Modal` | [NEW] | Radix `Dialog`. Used for job detail, upgrade prompt |
| `Sheet` | [NEW] | Slide-over from right. Job detail on mobile. |
| `Tabs` | [NEW] | Radix `Tabs`. Dashboard section switching. |
| `Progress` | EXTEND | Animate fit score bars. Add `glow` prop. |
| `Avatar` | [NEW] | Radix `Avatar`. With persona initials fallback. |
| `Tooltip` | [NEW] | Radix `Tooltip`. Hover info on score dimensions. |
| `Kbd` | [NEW] | Keyboard shortcut display. Used in command palette. |

### Dashboard-Specific

| Component | Description |
|---|---|
| `StatCard` | Metric + trend arrow + sparkline. Used on dashboard home. |
| `AgentStatusPill` | Green/orange/red dot + agent name + last-run time. Polling. |
| `ScoreMeter` | SVG circular dial, 0–100, animated fill on mount. |
| `JobCard` | Job title + company + fit score badge + platform logo + CTA. |
| `ApplicationRow` | Table row: job name, platform, status chip, date. Realtime-aware. |
| `SkillGapBar` | Horizontal bar with label + gap percentage + "Add to plan" button. |
| `PersonaCard` | Onboarding step 4. AI persona name + trait pills + select ring. |
| `PlatformTile` | Onboarding/settings Vault. LinkedIn/Indeed session status + connect CTA. |

### Layout Shell

| Component | Description |
|---|---|
| `Navbar` | Floating glassmorphism nav. Logo left. Links centre (desktop). Avatar+tier right. Transparent→blurred on scroll. |
| `Sidebar` | Dashboard left rail. Icons + labels. Collapses to icon-only on mobile. Active route glow. |
| `DashboardShell` | `Sidebar + main` wrapper. Handles responsive layout. |
| `OnboardingShell` | Step progress bar + back/next. Wraps all 7 onboarding steps. |
| `PermissionGate` | Renders blurred/locked feature UI for free users. Upgrade CTA overlay. |

