### [MODIFY] [Landing Page](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/(public)/page.tsx)
Complete rebuild with 8 sections:

#### Section 1 — Hero
- Full-viewport, centered
- Three.js orb (`ThreeDeeOrb`) in background (already built) — upgrade: add blue+violet particle shader
