### [MODIFY] [Login Page](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/(public)/login/page.tsx)
- Centered glass card on dark background
- `Sign in with Google` button (Lucide `Globe` icon)
- Small print: "Talvix uses Google OAuth. We never see your password."
- Redirects back to `/onboarding` or `/dashboard` based on profile completeness

### [NEW] Onboarding Flow
- **[MODIFY]** [src/app/onboarding/page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/onboarding/page.tsx) — wraps `OnboardingShell`; routes between steps via `?step=N` param
- 7 steps:
  1. **Persona** — 6 cards (Student / Early Career / Professional / Career Switcher / Returning / Freelancer). Framer Motion card flip on select.
  2. **Resume Upload** — Drag-drop zone with 6-layer security badge. Upload progress bar. Green tick on parse complete.
  3. **Target Roles** — Multi-select chip input. Server fetches `user_target_roles` suggestions. Max 5.
  4. **AI Persona** — 3 `PersonaCard` options generated by Agent 3 (fetched from Server 2). Select one.
  5. **Preferences** — City multi-select, Work mode (Remote/Hybrid/On-site), Salary range slider.
  6. **Profile Verification** — Summary card of all inputs. Edit links per section.
  7. **Vault** — `PlatformTile` for LinkedIn + Indeed. "Skip for now" option. Explains Tier 1 auto-apply.

