### [MODIFY] [/dashboard](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx) — Home
```
Grid layout:
┌──────────────────────┬────────────┐
│  Career Score Donut  │ Agent       │
│  (4 dimensions)      │ Heartbeat   │
├────────────┬─────────┤ (live 15)   │
│ Stat Cards │ Stat    │             │
│ (Applied   │ Cards   │             │
│  Today /   │(Month / ├────────────┤
│  Matches)  │ Streak) │ WA Status   │
├────────────┴─────────┴────────────┤
│  Top 3 Job Match Cards             │
└────────────────────────────────────┘
```
- Agent heartbeat: polls `GET /api/agents/status` every 30s via `useAgentStatus`
- Career score: `useCareerScore` → Recharts `RadarChart`
- Stat cards: `useApplicationStats`
- Job cards: `useJobs({ limit: 3 })` — top 3 by `fit_score`

