### React Query Hooks

| Hook | Endpoint | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `useUser` | `GET /api/auth/me` (Supabase) | User + profile |
| `useJobs` | `GET /api/dashboard` (Server 1) | Paginated, filterable |
| `useApplications` | Supabase direct query | + Realtime subscription |
| `useAgentStatus` | `GET /api/agents/status` (Server 1) | Poll 30s |
| `useCareerScore` | `GET /api/agents/career-intel` (Server 1) | Cached 1h |
| `useSkillGap` | `GET /api/agents/skill-gap` (Server 1) | Cached 1h |
| `useApplyCaps` | Derived from `useUser` | `daily_apply_count / daily_apply_limit` |
| `useWhatsAppStatus` | `GET /api/whatsapp/qr` (Server 1) | Poll 5s during onboarding |

