## Phase 5 — Next.js API Route Bridges

### [MODIFY] [/api/auth/callback](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/api/auth/callback/route.ts)
- Handles Supabase OAuth code exchange → sets session cookie → redirects to `/onboarding` or `/dashboard`

### [NEW] [/api/resume/upload](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/api/resume/upload/route.ts)
- Proxies multipart file upload to `Server 1 POST /api/resume/upload`
- Attaches `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>` and `X-Agent-Secret`
- Streams response back (progress events)

### [NEW] [/api/apply](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/app/api/apply/route.ts)
- `POST` with `{ job_id }` → proxies to `Server 1 POST /api/apply`
- Returns `{ status, message, queued_at }`

