## Wow-Factor Elements

### 1. Three.js Orb (Hero)
- Existing [ThreeDeeOrb.tsx](file:///C:/Users/DELL/Antigravity/Talvix/frontend/src/components/ui/ThreeDeeOrb.tsx) — upgrade: add blue+violet particle points orbiting a core sphere
- Subtle mouse-tracking tilt via `useMousePosition`

### 2. Agent Heartbeat Panel
- 15 cards in a grid, each pulsing when the agent ran in last 5 mins
- Color: green (active <5 min), orange (5–30 min), red (>30 min or failed)
- Data from `useAgentStatus` polling `GET /api/agents/status`

### 3. Live Apply Counter
- On Dashboard home: animated count-up showing `todayApplyCount` increasing in real time via Supabase Realtime
- "The AI applied to 3 jobs tonight" toast notification on login if jobs were applied overnight

### 4. Floating Mockup Cards (Landing Hero)
- Two glass cards floating around the orb (Framer Motion `float` animation)
- Card 1: `"Resume Tailored · Senior Product Manager ✓"` with score `87/100`
- Card 2: `"Auto-Applying · Indeed Easy Apply · 6 PM"` with animated dots

### 5. Onboarding Persona Flip
- Step 1 persona cards: hover triggers `rotateY(6deg)` + glow pulse
- Selected card: full blue border + checkmark overlay

