## Backend-to-Frontend API Contract Summary

| Frontend Call | Server 1 Endpoint | Auth Required |
|---|---|---|
| Resume upload | `POST /api/resume/upload` | JWT |
| Job feed | `GET /api/dashboard` | JWT |
| Apply to job | `POST /api/apply` (add this) | JWT |
| WhatsApp QR | `GET /api/whatsapp/qr` | JWT |
| Agent status | `GET /api/agents/status` (NEW) | JWT + Agent-Secret |
| Career intel | `GET /api/agents/career-intel` (proxy) | JWT |
| Skill gap | `GET /api/agents/skill-gap` (proxy) | JWT |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> `GET /api/agents/status` endpoint needs to be ADDED to Server 1. It queries the `agent_logs` table for the last-run timestamp and status of each agent. This is a new endpoint needed for the Agent Heartbeat panel.

